wasta-core-xenial (1.0.1) xenial; urgency=medium

  * debian/control: adding ubuntu-wallpapers-wily as recommends since
      contains Wasta-Linux default background
  * gschema.override: for Unity reverted back to Ambiance theme since
      Arc theme right click shadowing doesn't appear correctly in gedit,
      nautilus, etc.
  * app-install.sh: adding ubuntu-wallpapers-wily
  * wasta-reset: overhaul to reset all detected desktops (based on session
      files).
    - No longer replace current desktop, just inform user they need to
      restart to see the changes
    - Added initial Unity support

 -- Rik Shaw <rikshaw76@gmail.com>  Wed, 27 Apr 2016 14:06:41 +0300

